ActFirearms Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing a Contribution Agreement with the Province of Quebec
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness to ENTER INTO AN AGREEMENT with the province of Quebec providing for PAYMENT OF COMPENSATION in respect of administrative costs actually incurred by the province in relation to processing licenses, authorizations and applications for licenses and authorizations under the FIREARMS ACT.
